patthana23.35:1.1_0: Nauppanno nakusalo dhammo uppannassa kusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Ārammaṇe satta, adhipatiyā cha, upanissaye satta.
patthana23.35:2.1_0: Nauppanno naakusalo dhammo uppannassa akusalassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. Ārammaṇe cha, adhipatiyā cha, upanissaye cha.
patthana23.35:3.1_0: Naanupanno naabyākato dhammo uppannassa abyākatassa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo … tīṇi.
patthana23.35:4.1_0: Nauppanno naabyākato dhammo uppannassa abyākatassa dhammassa ārammaṇapaccayena paccayo. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana23.35:5.1_0: Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe satta, adhipatiyā cattāri, sahajāte nissaye tīṇi,
